descriptionHtml:
Any help to get this ingame will be greatly appreciated 

Help thread:
http://forums.nexusmods.com/index.php?/topic/629270-help-trying-to-get-custom-armor-model-ingame/

Included are:

the models in .3DS and .MAX

and the textures in .bmp


Users can modify my file; including releasing bug fixes or improving on the features my file adds to the game, and upload it as a seperate file, also can convert my file so that it works on similar games, and can use assets contained in my files in their own files.

But must credit Huke for the idea of Black Rock shooter.
